These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, disco, techno, classical
1. the fan of disco is between the fan of techno and the fan of classical##2
2. the fan of disco is on the left of the fan of techno##1
3. the fan of punk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |  3   |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | punk | classical | disco | techno |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, 7up, juice, coffee
1. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
3. the person drinking coffee is between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking milk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |  3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | 7up | coffee | milk | juice |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-3::.
4 different pets are kept: goat, hamster, guinea-pig, rabbit
1. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the owner of the hamster and the owner of the rabbit##2
3. the owner of the goat is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2    |  3   |   4    |
| Pet   | goat | rabbit | guinea-pig | hamster |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-4::.
