1. the person eating plum is between the person eating broccoli and the person eating onion##2
2. the person eating onion is on the right of the person eating plum##1
3. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Food   | spinach | broccoli | plum | onion |

